              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--ultramarine);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">YLT</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">And he turneth round his face unto the wall, and prayeth unto Jehovah, saying,</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--vermillion);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">ASV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">Then he turned<S>5437</S> his face<S>6440</S> to the wall<S>7023</S>, and prayed<S>6419</S> unto Jehovah<S>3068</S>, saying<S>559</S>,</span></div>
