              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--vermillion);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">ASV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">And I will add<S>3254</S> unto thy days<S>3117</S> fifteen<S>2568</S> years<S>8141</S>; and I will deliver<S>5337</S> thee and this city<S>5892</S> out of the hand<S>3709</S> of the king<S>4428</S> of Assyria<S>804</S>; and I will defend<S>1598</S> this city<S>5892</S> for mine own sake<S>5650</S>, and for my servant David<S>1732</S>'s sake.</span></div>
