            <div style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;padding-bottom:1.5rem;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(197,150,12,0.15);">
              <div style="font-family:var(--font-heading);color:var(--gold);font-size:0.85rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;font-weight:600;">2 Kings 20:11</div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--leather-dark);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">KJV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">And Isaiah the prophet cried unto the LORD: and he brought the shadow ten degrees backward, by which it had gone down in the dial of Ahaz.</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--ultramarine);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">YLT</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">And Isaiah the prophet calleth unto Jehovah, and He bringeth back the shadow by the degrees that it had gone down in the degrees of Ahaz -- backward ten degrees.</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--vermillion);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">ASV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">And Isaiah<S>3470</S> the prophet<S>5030</S> cried<S>7121</S> unto Jehovah<S>3068</S>; and he brought<S>7725</S> the shadow<S>6738</S> ten<S>6235</S> steps<S>4609</S> backward<S>322</S>, by<S>4609</S> which it had gone down<S>3381</S> on the dial<S>4609</S> of Ahaz<S>271</S>.</span></div>
              <div><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--verdigris, #4a7c59);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">WEB</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">Isaiah the prophet cried to Yahweh; and he brought the shadow ten steps backward, by which it had gone down on the sundial of Ahaz.</span></div>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;padding-bottom:1.5rem;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(197,150,12,0.15);">
              <div style="font-family:var(--font-heading);color:var(--gold);font-size:0.85rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;font-weight:600;">2 Kings 20:12</div>
