              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--ultramarine);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">YLT</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">Lo, days are coming, and borne hath been all that [is] in thy house, and that thy father have treasured up till this day, to Babylon; there is not left a thing, said Jehovah;</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--vermillion);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">ASV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">Behold<S>3117</S>, the days come<S>935</S>, that all that is in thy house<S>1004</S>, and that which thy fathers<S>1</S> have laid up in store<S>686</S> unto this day<S>3117</S>, shall be carried<S>5375</S> to Babylon<S>894</S>: nothing<S>1697</S> shall be left<S>3498</S>, saith<S>559</S> Jehovah<S>3068</S>.</span></div>
