              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--ultramarine);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">YLT</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">and of thy sons who go out from thee, whom thou begettest, they take away, and they have been eunuchs in the palace of the king of Babylon.'</span></div>
